title: THE DANNY THOMAS SHOW -- Pupa From Italy ( 11th Season )
description: This 1964 episode is actually the second of 4 shows with lesser-known teenage Italian pop singer Piccola Pupa, who in the previous season played Maria in one episode of a story arc where Danny and Kathy Williams were on a European tour. I don't have that one or any of the 10th Season, but in this episode Maria was renamed Pupa...who just arrived in the United States
